    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是经典的Clean Architecture分层。那presentation到domain、domain到data都是单向依赖对吧？另外，这三层具体在App里对应什么模块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "presentation",
